‚≠ê MODULE 19 ‚Äî PART 1
LIVE VISITOR MAP (Realtime Location Tracking)

Uses IP ‚Üí Geo lookup ‚Üí WebSocket broadcast.

API Route

app/api/visitor/ping/route.ts

import { pushAnalytics } from "@/lib/matrix/analytics";
import { NextResponse } from "next/server";

export async function GET(req: Request) {
  const ip = req.headers.get("x-forwarded-for") || "0.0.0.0";

  // Fake geolocation for demo, real route calls geo service
  const geo = {
    country: "United States",
    city: "Atlanta",
    region: "Georgia"
  };

  pushAnalytics({
    type: "visitor-location",
    ip,
    ...geo
  });

  return NextResponse.json({ ok: true });
}

Frontend Ping (fires automatically):

components/visitor/VisitorPing.tsx

"use client";

import { useEffect } from "react";

export default function VisitorPing() {
