‚≠ê MODULE 19 ‚Äî PART 2
LIVE VISITOR MAP UI (Inside THE MATRIX)

Realtime map updated via analytics stream.

components/matrix/VisitorMap.tsx

"use client";

import useAnalyticsStream from "@/lib/matrix/useAnalyticsStream";
import { useEffect, useState } from "react";

export default function VisitorMap() {
  const events = useAnalyticsStream();
  const [locations, setLocations] = useState([]);

  useEffect(() => {
    const locs = events.filter((e) => e.type === "visitor-location");
    setLocations(locs.slice(0, 50));
  }, [events]);

  return (
    <div className="bg-black/40 p-6 rounded-xl border border-teal-500">
      <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-300 mb-4">
        Live Visitor Map
      </h2>

      <div className="space-y-3">
        {locations.map((l, i) => (
          <div key={i} className="flex justify-between text-teal-200">
            <span>{l.city}, {l.region}</span>
            <span>{l.country}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}


Shadow PRIME now knows who‚Äôs visiting and from where.

‚≠ê MODULE 19 ‚Äî PART 3
VISITOR PROFILE AI (Behavioral Analyzer)

Shadow PRIME will classify every visitor based on:

