‚≠ê MODULE 20 ‚Äî PART 1
THE MASTER ORCHESTRATOR (The ‚ÄúPrime Kernel‚Äù)

This is the central node that ALL modules report to and receive commands from.

File: lib/shadow/os/kernel.ts
import { useShadowOS } from "./state";
import { applyAvatarState } from "../avatarEngine";
import { runSelfCheck } from "./selfcheck";
import { autoOptimize } from "./autoOptimize";
import { interpretCommand } from "@/lib/matrix/lucid/interpret";
import { applyAction } from "@/lib/matrix/lucid/actions";
import { pushAnalytics } from "@/lib/matrix/analytics";

export async function ShadowPrimeKernel(event) {
  const os = useShadowOS.getState();

  switch (event.type) {
    case "voice-command":
      const parsed = await interpretCommand(event.input);
      await applyAction(parsed);
      os.setResponse(parsed.action);
      pushAnalytics({ type: "prime-executed", event: parsed });
      break;

    case "avatar-output":
      applyAvatarState(event.text);
      break;

    case "system-selfcheck":
      await runSelfCheck();
      break;

    case "optimize":
      await autoOptimize();
      break;

    case "analytics-event":
      os.setSystemEvent(event.payload);
      break;

    default:
      pushAnalytics({ type: "prime-unknown-event", event });
  }
}


This is the kernel ‚Äî the heart of Shadow PRIME OS.
Everything flows through it.

‚≠ê MODULE 20 ‚Äî PART 2
GLOBAL EVENT BUS (All Modules Connected)

Every module reports to the kernel through the event bus.

File: components/os/EventBus.tsx
"use client";

import { useEffect } from "react";
import { ShadowPrimeKernel } from "@/lib/shadow/os/kernel";

export default function EventBus() {
  useEffect(() => {
    const handler = (e) => ShadowPrimeKernel(e.detail);

    window.addEventListener("shadow-event", handler);
    window.addEventListener("shadow-speak", (e) =>
      ShadowPrimeKernel({ type: "voice-command", input: e.detail })
    );

    return () => window.removeEventListener("shadow-event", handler);
  }, []);

  return null;
}


Now EVERYTHING in the site can send events:

avatar

world

UI

behavior trackers

analytics

admin Matrix

voice commands

store actions

livestream

sound engine

OS global timers

All talking to the same brain.

