‚≠ê MODULE 23 ‚Äî PART 4
üíæ THE AUTO-COMMIT + AUTO-PUSH PIPELINE (No Questions Asked)

Shadow PRIME commits & pushes every successful update.

File: lib/shadow/git/autoPush.ts
import { execSync } from "child_process";

export async function autoPush(message) {
  execSync("git add .");
  execSync(`git commit -m "${message}" || echo 'nothing to commit'`);
  execSync("git push origin main");
}


This runs after every action:

await autoPush("Shadow PRIME auto-update: " + action.summary);

